
Overview of noun radiance

The noun radiance has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (2) radiance, glow, glowing -- (the amount of electromagnetic radiation leaving or arriving at a point on a surface)
2. (1) radiance, radiancy, shine, effulgence, refulgence, refulgency -- (the quality of being bright and sending out rays of light)
3. radiance -- (an attractive combination of good health and happiness; "the radiance of her countenance")
